Tuvima.WikidataReconciliation
Copyright (c) 2026 Tuvima

This library's reconciliation algorithms (dual-search strategy, scoring formula,
fuzzy matching approach, type checking, and property matching) are based on
openrefine-wikibase by Antonin Delpeuch, licensed under the MIT License.

  Original repository: https://github.com/wetneb/openrefine-wikibase
  Academic paper: Antonin Delpeuch. "A survey of OpenRefine reconciliation services."
                  https://arxiv.org/abs/1906.08092

The nfdi4culture fork informed the configurable Wikibase endpoint support:
  https://gitlab.com/nfdi4culture/openrefine-reconciliation-services/openrefine-wikibase

This is an independent C# implementation — no code was copied from the original
Python project. The algorithms were re-implemented from the documented behavior
and public API specifications.
